# SELLTHISBOOK
 
MAKE A VERSION IN LATEX OR WORD OF THIS BOOK!

CREATE A PDF WHICH IS PRINTABLE IN LETTER SIZE!

ASK PEOPLE TO PRINT OUT A COPY!

PRINT THE WHOLE BOOK BY HAND WITH MARKER ON CARDBOARD!

SELL THE BOOK TO PASSERBY ON THE STREET FROM THE [TRASHCARTS](scrolls/TRASHCARTS)!

MAKE A 6X9 INCH VERSION!

USE IT TO CREATE A BOOK TO SELL ON [LULU PRESS PRINT ON DEMAND PUBLISHERS](https://www.lulu.com/)!

USE YOUR WINNINGS TO PRINT MORE COPIES OF THE BOOK, AND PUT THOSE COPIES IN BOOK STORES FOR FREE AS A BOOK GUERILLA!  
